Interface Entity

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LightEmmiter, LightSensorRobot, LineColliderEntity, SimpleRobot, StaticBlock, Wall, Whisker, WhiskerRobot

    public interface Entity
extends java.io.Serializable
    Interface implemented by Entities. Entities are defined as any object that can be rendered, collided with, and updated.
    Author:
    L. L. Blumire
